title: YSDN student designers score big in international awards (York University)
text: ( Source : York University ) The York University/ Sheridan College joint program in Design (YSDN) makes history once again, with recent graduate Joyce Dang (BDes '15) bringing home the Adobe Design Achievement Awards ( ADAA ) prize for packaging.
